  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Future of Combat is Here!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the unique mechanics of drone control, where technology becomes the core of your strategy. <i>Drone Strike: Engineer Simulator </i>puts you in charge of an advanced drone to tackle the toughest missions. Command, strike, and hit targets with precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/e6a834d5d80384abd3c745877d6b33e5.poster.avif?t=1771853352\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/e6a834d5d80384abd3c745877d6b33e5.webm?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Missions to Test Your Limits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face challenges where your drone is your last line of defense. From fierce combat operations to civilian tasks, each level is a new test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/d330e9ee4d1ee4e06b4fa3436f427a2a.poster.avif?t=1771853352\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/d330e9ee4d1ee4e06b4fa3436f427a2a.webm?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Drone, Your Style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your drone to match your playstyle! Choose weapons suited to any mission, add unique colors and designs. Make your drone your signature in the field!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/a700a6e94e9105a380a50b1c3dfc441c.poster.avif?t=1771853352\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/a700a6e94e9105a380a50b1c3dfc441c.webm?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/a700a6e94e9105a380a50b1c3dfc441c.mp4?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Future of Combat is Here!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master the unique mechanics of drone control, where technology becomes the core of your strategy. <i>Drone Strike: Engineer Simulator </i>puts you in charge of an advanced drone to tackle the toughest missions. Command, strike, and hit targets with precision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/e6a834d5d80384abd3c745877d6b33e5.poster.avif?t=1771853352\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/e6a834d5d80384abd3c745877d6b33e5.webm?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Missions to Test Your Limits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face challenges where your drone is your last line of defense. From fierce combat operations to civilian tasks, each level is a new test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/d330e9ee4d1ee4e06b4fa3436f427a2a.poster.avif?t=1771853352\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/d330e9ee4d1ee4e06b4fa3436f427a2a.webm?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Drone, Your Style</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your drone to match your playstyle! Choose weapons suited to any mission, add unique colors and designs. Make your drone your signature in the field!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/a700a6e94e9105a380a50b1c3dfc441c.poster.avif?t=1771853352\" width=618 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/a700a6e94e9105a380a50b1c3dfc441c.webm?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475450/extras/a700a6e94e9105a380a50b1c3dfc441c.mp4?t=1771853352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
